canvasbio-cb2000
================

Copyright (C) 2025-2026 Kristofer Pagnussat

This repository publishes the standalone CanvasBio CB2000 driver package for
libfprint, including the main driver sources, the SIGFM matcher path, the
OpenCV feature-mosaic helper, and the associated build/session/report scripts.

The repository license text is provided in `LICENSE` as LGPL-2.1.
The driver source files themselves declare LGPL-2.1-or-later where applicable.
